        main
            .container
                h6 Frequently Asked Questions
                h3 What is GroceryGo?
                p GroceryGo is an e-commerce platform offering a wide range of groceries and household products.

                h3 Do you offer any loyalty program?
                p Yes! We have a loyalty program. For more details, please click [here](/loyalty-program).

                h3 What payment methods do you accept?
                p We accept Cash on Delivery, Online Visa/MasterCard, Credit/Debit Card On Delivery, and UnionPay Debit/Credit Cards.

                h3 I am having trouble verifying my account. What should I do?
                p If you are experiencing issues with OTP SMS, please call our helpline (021) 111-624-333 from the same mobile number. Our CSR will assist with account verification.

                h3 Do you ship orders across Pakistan?
                p Yes, we deliver to over 800 cities in Pakistan.

                h3 How much are the delivery charges?
                p Please visit the [Delivery & Shipping](/delivery-info) page for detailed information.

                h3 How can I track my order status?
                p You can check the status of your order from the 'My Orders' screen in your account or through the Order Tracking page.

                h3 How do I return a product?
                p For information on returning a product, please visit the [Returns & Refunds](/returns-refunds) page.

                h3 Are there any shipping charges for returns?
                p No, shipping charges for returns are not applicable.

                h3 Can I return a product after 7 days?
                p Returns must be initiated within 7 days of delivery. We cannot accept return requests after this period.

                h3 Do you verify orders before processing?
                p Yes, our customer service team will call you to verify the order before processing it.

                h3 What is your warranty policy?
                p Warranty policies vary by vendor and product. GroceryGo does not handle warranty claims directly. These are processed through the vendor's service centers. If a product includes a warranty, it will be stated in the product specifications or description.

